<div id="how-it-works" class="how-it-works-container background-white" style="background-image: url('<%=cl_image_path("poncho/bici.jpg")%>')">
  <div class="how-it-works-section">
    <div class="how-it-works-section-title padding-bottom-mid flex-center flex-justify-center padding-top-mid">
      <h2 class="banner-title">¿Cómo funciona?</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center">
      <div class="flex-center flex-justify-around display-block-mobile">
        <div class="step-description">
          <a href="<%= "#" %>">
            <div class="icon padding-bottom-small">
              <%= image_tag "selecciona.svg", class:"avatar-big"%>
            </div>
          </a>
          <div class="avatar-big mid-font padding-bottom-small">
            <p>Selecciona el tipo de vehículo poncho a rentar, patineta o bicicleta.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-description">
          <div class="icon padding-bottom-small">
            <%= image_tag "datos.svg", class:"avatar-big"%>
          </div>
          <div class="avatar-big mid-font padding-bottom-small">
            <p>Llena algunos datos y paga el primer mes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-description">
          <div class="icon padding-bottom-small">
            <%= image_tag "reserva.svg", class:"avatar-big"%>
          </div>
          <div class="avatar-big mid-font padding-bottom-small">
            <p>Separamos un vehículo Poncho para ti.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-description">
          <div class="icon padding-bottom-small">
            <%= image_tag "recibes.svg", class:"avatar-big"%>
          </div>
          <div class="avatar-big mid-font padding-bottom-small">
            <p>Lo enviamos a tú casa en un máximo de 24 horas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step-description">
          <div class="icon padding-bottom-small">
            <%= image_tag "disfruta.svg", class:"avatar-big"%>
          </div>
          <div class="avatar-big mid-font padding-bottom-small">
            <p>Empiezas a ser sostenible y tienes todo un mes para disfrutar</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <hr style="border: 2px solid #8bcfa3; margin-right: 30%; margin-left: 30%;">
    <div class="padding-top-mid padding-bottom-mid">
      <div class="flex-center flex-justify-center">
        <div class="padding-left-big padding-left-mid  mobile-hidden">
          <%= link_to "RESERVA LA TUYA", plans_path, class: "button2 banner-call-to-actions" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="product-condditions-list flex-center flex-justify-center">
        <div class="list-container">
          <div class="product-item flex-center">
            <i class="fas fa-check fa-sm"> </i>
            <div class="padding-left-xsmall">
              <p class="product-item-text">Sin cláusulas de permanencia</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="product-item flex-center">
            <i class="fas fa-check fa-sm"> </i>
            <div class="padding-left-xsmall">
              <p class="product-item-text">Sin contratos</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="product-item flex-center">
            <i class="fas fa-check fa-sm"> </i>
            <div class="padding-left-xsmall">
              <p class="product-item-text">Cancela cuando quieras</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center padding-left-big desktop-hidden button-height margin-top-big">
        <%= link_to "RESERVA LA TUYA", plans_path, class: "button2 banner-call-to-actions" %>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
